\subsection{Hybrid Scoring Engine}

The hybrid engine sits between the Naive Bayes output and the API response. Its job is to catch cases where the statistical model was misled---typically by phishing emails written in deliberately polite or professional language---and correct the prediction using the additional signals we have available.

